  --- The WebAppContext 9623
  The WebAppContext handler is an extension of ContextHandler that  coordinates the construction and configuration of nested handlers:    ConstraintSecurityHandler  ,   SessionHandler    and   ServletHandler  .  The handlers are configured by pluggable configuration classes, with  the default being    WebXmlConfiguration   and    JettyWebXmlConfiguration  .        <div class="su
